{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bafdd909de","title":"中央关于补报重大贪污犯的处理情况致薄一波、刘澜涛电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"af32597cf8","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":1,"articleId":"bafdd909de"}],"tags":[{"id":"3dcf7883ce","name":"刘澜涛","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"bc1d1ca3a9","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bafdd909de","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"薄一波，当时任中共中央华北局第一书记。刘澜涛，当时任中共中央华北局第三书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7fd7255439","type":"title","text":"中央关于补报重大资污犯的处理情况致薄一波、刘澜涛电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bafdd909de"},{"id":"bc1d1ca3a9","type":"paragraph","text":"薄一波、刘澜涛同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bafdd909de"},{"id":"c5b5f7a721","type":"paragraph","text":"你们十一月二十八日关于华北方面发现的贪污事件的报告收到了。在这个报告中没有说到对于那些重大贪污犯，党和政府是如何处理的，请你们将处理的情况补告我们，即对太原市区委书记赵城、区长任华，唐山市粮食公司负责人（报告中无姓名），河北徐水县银行经理赵增非，山西交城县长张进才，辽东工业厅驻津办事处主任刘治宇，山西交通局保管科副科长赵以焦，华北军区后勤部汽车学校政治委员季普吾，河北省供销社西北小组负责人（报告中无姓名）等重大贪污犯判处了何种罪刑，向我们作一补充的报告","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bafdd909de"},{"id":"e8cf8cd079","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bafdd909de"},{"id":"0cf28ff997","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年十二月一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bafdd909de"}],"page":{"id":"f256a4ffc5","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bafdd909de","start":100,"end":100}}}},"__N_SSG":true}